{"tid":520752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪維斯:中國的球員和你拼的不是技術 , 而是身體對抗 , 但他們又沒有想像中般強壯 ","createTime":"2018-01-05T17:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T20:52:51.000Z","uid":123787,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7d5a1ab771e4c3381f5a716f42581ccdc8876f","tid":520752,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"&quot;中國的球員和你拼的不是技術 , 而是身體對抗 , 但他們又沒有想像中般強壯 , 而且他們技術粗糙和缺乏經驗 , 不懂得點到即止 , 所以犯規時下腳往往很重令你受傷。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;雖然近年中超收購不少歐洲聯賽球星 , 但要中超追上歐洲的一線聯賽 , 我相信50年內是做不到。當中不只是聯賽的技術含量 , 也包括球迷如何看待這個聯賽 ; 而且中超也不應只注重外援 , 他們應該也從年輕球員出發 , 提早讓他們上陣吸收經驗 , 這點要依靠中超的政策了。&quot;"},{"pid":"5dd73ab20f8f58194fc981c8c0c36dcc23163050","tid":520752,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b56e05449dd6e7b98e81e9c18bbcd4bcfcb80e2","tid":520752,"uid":144466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"ok下場準備斷腳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03154f674b7cd16abdb700fee499fe992bbccb82","tid":520752,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b56e05449dd6e7b98e81e9c18bbcd4bcfcb80e2","tid":520752,"uid":144466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"ok下場準備斷腳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"應該上場前就斷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f84429848fe3415d1ecd9346db9a6a813d6af","tid":520752,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b56e05449dd6e7b98e81e9c18bbcd4bcfcb80e2","tid":520752,"uid":144466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"ok下場準備斷腳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T18:12:2